sources.title: The Irish Connection | Full Movie | Action Adventure
sources.description:
The Irish Connection - A female British agent Aureille is sent to Ireland to investigate the robbery of Bearer Bonds by Rory Baker. Betrayed and set up by a Priest, the agent goes Rogue in Malta, dodging the Baker's ruthless hit men and worse, her own boss Miranda.
2022.  Stars: Flora Spencer-Longhurst, Rosa Coduri, Matt Healy
